  "rationale": "This supervisor prioritizes rapid marker acquisition and approach, robust obstacle avoidance, and prevents oscillations by assigning clear, non-overlapping escape and search behaviors. Helper states ensure atomic actions (move, rotate, scan, track) are one-shot, and transitions are deterministic. Marker tracking is prioritized when visible, with fallback to scan/search if lost. Obstacle recovery always passes through a scan before resuming exploration.",
