  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: immediately switch to marker_track and approach when detected.",
    "If marker_lost during tracking/approach, switch to scan_full to reacquire marker.",
    "In clear, alternate between forward_commit and scan_full to balance exploration and marker search.",
    "Obstacle states (obs_front, obs_left, obs_right) trigger escape via scan_full or a single preferred rotation, never both directions to avoid oscillation.",
    "After obstacle recovery, always pass through scan_full before resuming exploration.",
    "Commit states (forward_commit, rotate_commit_cw/ccw, scan_full) are one-shot: after action, return to clear or appropriate decision state.",
    "When marker_close is detected in any state, transition to goal_stop and only allow stop.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state for totality and safety.",
    "No infinite controllable loops; all helper/action states transition out after their primary action.",
    "No move_forward allowed from obs_front; recovery is always via scan or rotation."
  ]
